'''线粒体分裂'''是[[线粒体|线粒体]]增殖的过程，在[[真核细胞|真核细胞]]内持续进行并受到高度调控。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = H Sesaki, RE Jensen
 | title = Division versus fusion: Dnm1p and Fzo1p antagonistically regulate mitochondrial shape
 | journal = Journal of Cell Biology
 | volume = 147
 | issue = 4
 | pages = 699-706
 | doi = 
 | pmid = 10562274
 | pmc = 2156171
 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2156171/
 | language = en |date=Nov 15, 1999}}</ref>线粒体它使得[[细胞|细胞]]内不同区域的线粒体明确分工，<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Collins T, Berridge M, Lipp P
 | title = Mitochondria are morphologically and functionally heterogeneous within cells
 | journal =  European Molecular Biology Organization Journal 
 | volume = 21
 | issue = 7
 | pages = 1616-1627
 | doi = 10.1093/emboj/21.7.1616
 | id=PMCID 11927546
 | pmc = 125942
 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC125942/pdf/cdf156.pdf
 | language = en |date=Apr 2, 2002}}</ref>并分裂在线粒体分布方面有重要作用（对[[细胞分裂|细胞分裂]]后保证线粒体传递到[[子细胞|子细胞]]中尤为关键）。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = 蒋春笋、肖伟明、陈佺
 | title = 线粒体分裂、融合与细胞凋亡
 | journal = 生物物理学报
 | year = 2007
 | month = 
 | volume = 23
 | issue = 4
 | pages = 256-264
 | url = http://d.wanfangdata.com.cn/Periodical_swwlxb200704005.aspx
 | language = zh }}</ref>为了保证在细胞发生分裂后每个[[子细胞|子细胞]]都能继承[[母细胞|母细胞]]的线粒体，母细胞中的线粒体在一个[[细胞周期|细胞周期]]需要至少复制一次。即使是在不再分裂的细胞内，线粒体为了填补已老化的线粒体造成的空缺也需要进行分裂。<ref>{{cite book
